urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.206#Then in answer the goddess grey-eyed Athene spoke to him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.207#'I have come down to stay your anger--but will you obey me?--
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.208#from the sky; and the goddess of the white arms Hera sent me,
