urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.210#Come then, do not take your sword in your hand, keep clear of fighting,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.211#though indeed with words you may abuse him, and it will be that way.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.212#And this also will I tell you and it will be a thing accomplished.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.213#Some day three times over such shining gifts shall be given you
