urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.215#Then in answer again spoke Achilleus of the swift feet:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.216#'Goddess, it is necessary that I obey the word of you two,
