urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.218#If any man obeys the gods, they listen to him also.'
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.219#He spoke, and laid his heavy hand on the silver sword hilt
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.220#and thrust the great blade back into the scabbard nor disobeyed
