urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.240#some day longing for Achilleus will come to the sons of the Achaians,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.241#all of them. Then stricken at heart though you be, you will be able
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:1.242#to do nothing, when in their numbers before man-slaughtering Hektor
