urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.70#'Go now swiftly to the host of the Achaians and Trojans
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.71#and try to make it so that the Trojans are first offenders
