urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.85#Thus would murmur any man, Achaian or Trojan.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.86#She in the likeness of a man merged among the Trojans assembled,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.87#Laodokos, Antenor's son, a powerful spearman,
