urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.182#Thus shall a man speak: then let the wide earth open to take me.'
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.183#Then in encouragement fair-haired Menelaos spoke to him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:4.184#'Do not fear, nor yet make afraid the Achaian people.
