urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.447#For I know this thing well in my heart, and my mind knows it:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.448#there will come a day when sacred Ilion shall perish,
