urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.459#and some day seeing you shedding tears a man will say of you:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.460#"This is the wife of Hektor, who was ever the bravest fighter
