urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.478#great in strength, as am I, and rule strongly over Ilion;
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.479#and some day let them say of him: "He is better by far than his father",
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.480#as he comes in from the fighting; and let him kill his enemy
