urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.516#before turning away from the place where he had talked with his lady.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.517#It was Alexandros the godlike who first spoke to him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.518#'Brother, I fear that I have held back your haste, by being
