urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.520#Then tall Hektor of the shining helm spoke to him in answer:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:6.521#'Strange man! There is no way that one, giving judgment in fairness,
