urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:8.1#Now Dawn the yellow-robed scattered over all the earth. Zeus
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:8.2#who joys in the thunder made an assembly of all the immortals
