urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:8.38#Then Zeus the gatherer of the clouds smiled at her and answered:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:8.39#'Tritogeneia, dear daughter, do not lose heart; for I say this
