urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.370#pulled his bow against Tydeus' son, the shepherd of the people,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.371#leaning against the column, work of men's hand, on the gravemound
