urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.411#While he was pondering these things in his heart and his spirit
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.412#the ranks of the armoured Trojans came on against him, and penned him
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.413#in their midst, but made thereby a wound in their ranks, as when
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.414#closing about a wild boar the hounds and the lusty young men
