urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.462#Three times he called, as much voice as a man's head could hold,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.463#and three times Menelaos the warlike heard him shouting
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:11.464#and immediately spoke to Aias, who was near by him:
