urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.41#Now powerful Agamemnon spoke aloud and addressed him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.42#'Nestor, son of Neleus, great glory of the Achaians,
