urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.44#I am afraid huge Hektor may accomplish that word against me
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.45#that he spoke, threatening, among the Trojans assembled,
