urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.59#from which side the Achaians are broken into confusion,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.60#so indiscriminately are they killed, and their crying goes skyward.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.61#We then must take thought together how these things shall be done
