urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.210#I shall be forever called honoured by them, and beloved.'
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:14.211#Then in turn Aphrodite the laughing answered her:
