urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.77#from his hated head; no, but the voice of murderous Hektor
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.78#calling to the Trojans crashes about my ears; with their war cry
