urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.599#thunderously, and the closing sorrow came over the Achaians
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.600#as the great man went down, but the Trojans were gladdened greatly
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.601#and came and stood in a pack about him, nor did the Achaians
