urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.637#as the swords and leaf-headed spears stabbed against them. No longer
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.638#could a man, even a knowing one, have made out the godlike
