urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.640#a mass of weapons, the blood and the dust, while others about him
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.641#kept forever swarming over his dead body, as flies
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.642#through a sheepfold thunder about the pails overspilling
