urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.702#Three times Patroklos tried to mount the angle of the towering
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:16.703#wall, and three times Phoibos Apollo battered him backward
