urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.242#No sooner was the order given than the thing had been done.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.243#They brought back seven tripods from the shelter, those Agamemnon
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.244#had promised, and twenty shining cauldrons, twelve horses. They brought back
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.245#immediately the seven women the work of whose hands was
