urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.249#They brought these into the midst of assembly, and Agamemnon
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.250#stood up, and Talthybios in voice like an immortal
