urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.359#so now in their thickness the pride of the helms bright shining
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.360#were carried out from the ships, and shields massive in the middle
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.361#and the corselets strongly hollowed and the ash spears were worn forth.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.362#The shining swept to the sky and all earth was laughing about them
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:19.363#under the glitter of bronze and beneath their feet stirred the thunder
