urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.98#Deeply troubled he spoke to his own great-hearted spirit:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.99#'Ah me! If I go now inside the wall and the gateway,
