urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.108#Thus they will speak; and as for me, it would be much better
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.109#at that time, to go against Achilleus, and slay him, and come back,
