urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.167#First to speak among them was the father of gods and mortals:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.168#'Ah me, this is a man beloved whom now my eyes watch
