urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.179#Do you wish to bring back a man who is mortal, one long since
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.180#doomed by his destiny, from ill-sounding death and release him?
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.181#Do it, then; but not all the rest of us gods shall approve you.'
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.182#Then Zeus the gatherer of the clouds spoke to her in answer:
