urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.214#But the goddess grey-eyed Athene came now to Peleion
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.215#and stood close beside him and addressed him in winged words: 'Beloved
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.216#of Zeus, shining Achilleus, I am hopeful now that you and I
