urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.311#Hektor made his swoop, swinging his sharp sword, and Achilleus
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.312#charged, the heart within him loaded with savage fury.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.313#In front of his chest the beautiful elaborate great shield
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.314#covered him, and with the glittering helm with four horns
