urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.337#In his weakness Hektor of the shining helm spoke to him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.338#'I entreat you, by your life, by your knees, by your parents,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.339#do not let the dogs feed on me by the ships of the Achaians,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.340#but take yourself the bronze and gold that are there in abundance,
