urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.387#Patroklos: and I will not forget him, never so long as
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.388#I remain among the living and my knees have their spring beneath me.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:22.389#And though the dead forget the dead in the house of Hades,
