urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.626#'Yes, child: all this you said to me was true as you said it.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.627#My limbs are no longer steady, dear friend; not my feet, neither
