urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.641#Now these sons of Aktor were twins; one held the reins at his leisure,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.642#held the reins at his leisure while the other lashed on the horses.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.643#This was I, once. Now it is for the young men to encounter
