urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.646#Go now, and honour the death of your companion with contests.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.647#I accept this from you gratefully, and my heart is happy
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.648#that you have remembered me and my kindness, that I am not forgotten
