urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.666#He laid his hand on the hard-working jenny, and spoke out:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.667#'Let the man come up who will carry off the two-handled goblet.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.668#I say no other of the Achaians will beat me at boxing
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.669#and lead off the jenny. I claim I am the champion. Is it not
