urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.728#fell on his chest as the people gazed upon them and wondered.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:23.729#Next, brilliant much-enduring Odysseus endeavoured to lift him
