urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.39#No, you gods; your desire is to help this cursed Achilleus
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.40#within whose breast there are no feelings of justice, nor can
