urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.472#where Achilleus the beloved of Zeus was sitting. He found him
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.473#inside, and his companions were sitting apart, as two only,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.474#Automedon the hero and Alkimos, scion of Ares,
