urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.577#and led inside the herald, the old king's crier, and gave him
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.578#a chair to sit in, then from the smooth-polished mule wagon
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.wheng:24.579#lifted out the innumerable spoils for the head of Hektor,
